{"tid":1551780,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"兄弟加油。 對家崩潰才叫贏","createTime":"2019-09-08T07:19:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T07:51:18.000Z","uid":283725,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e5d0f790720e6e86244d0c679740a2258e9f00ff","tid":1551780,"uid":283725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:19:28.000Z","msg":"菲律賓總統杜特爾特（Rodrigo Duterte）上周訪華，並與中國國家主席習近平見面，昨日杜特爾特進行電視講話時提到，他與習近平談論南海主權爭議問題。杜特爾特稱，他感受到習近平因為香港示威問題，承受不小的壓力，因此情緒變得很衝動。杜特爾特又稱，習近平沒辦法心平氣和地解決南海問題，現在他正在尋找「開戰」以外的解決辦法。"},{"pid":"644c0f70c07363000553cb553370e1c5e13735ec","tid":1551780,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:20:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a8ce0a177afafe6a5e536f6692c8a673ed379f6","tid":1551780,"uid":63757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:23:08.000Z","msg":"氣急敗壞啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1618f72ec145527c6be7eb2d1ac5c7abd4185def","tid":1551780,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:51:18.000Z","msg":"小學雞嬲豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}